Hello, welcome to Harmony Music School. My name is Russell Foster, and I will be assisting you today. May I have your name, please?

Hi Russell, my name is Rose Long.

Nice to meet you, Rose! How can I help you with your concern about our privacy policy?

I was surprised to find out what information is being collected. Could you clarify what personal data you need from me?

Of course, Rose. We need your phone number so that we can contact you regarding class schedules or cancellations. Could you provide that, please?

Certainly, it's one two three, four five six, seven eight nine zero.

Thank you, Rose. We also require your email address to send you our monthly newsletter and updates. Could you share that with me?

Sure, my email is rose.long at example dot com.

Great, thank you for that information. Rest assured, all data is secured to protect your privacy. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

No, that's all I needed to know. Thank you for clarifying, Russell.

You're welcome, Rose. Thank you for your time, and if you have any other questions, feel free to contact us. Have a great day!
